Installation

Download the binary at https://github.com/webmproject/WebPShop/releases.
Direct link for Windows x64: https://github.com/webmproject/WebPShop/releases/download/v0.4.3/WebPShop_0_4_3_Win_x64.8bi
Direct link for MacOS (extract the ZIP archive afterwise): https://github.com/webmproject/WebPShop/releases/download/v0.4.2/WebPShop_0_4_2_Mac_Universal.zip
Move the plug-in (the .8bi binary for Windows or the .plugin folder for MacOS) to the Photoshop plug-in directory (C:\Program Files\Common Files\Adobe\Plug-Ins\CC for Windows, /Library/Application Support/Adobe/Plug-Ins/CC for Mac). Run Photoshop.